{
  "stem": "25287.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then nobody see us, to the rail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this man wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But was a open wagon, some Yugoslav people just barely stop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they let us, to climb to this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you know, one day we went this train, and stop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we needed to wait.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was on the one bridge, you know, because it was in-- it wasn't too hot, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, young Russian people-- you know, that was already end of the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And because one of our lager sisters speaked fluently, German, so they don't want to believe that we are not German womans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We don't have the number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So one-- one Russian man, one officer, said-- because was talking, back and forth-- if you Jewish, then you know the Shema.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That's the reason I would like all the Jewish children to learn the Shema, especially all grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "When Jacob was three years old, I start to teach him Shema Israel, [SPEAKING HEBREW], just this much.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And if we don't know that, I don't think so, we-- we get away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You know, a soldier is a soldier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He give some paper to us, and asking people, Joint-- Joint, or other city, them help us to get back Budapest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And how I said to you, one day we was waiting for come a train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So finally, we arrived to Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they said have a Hungarian place, a Jewish, not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And middle of the night, I heard Hungarian anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we went to the Joint, and they said, wait for two days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We give you some new clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
